0
00:00:11,039 --> 00:00:12,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你可真是个笨蛋</font>

1
00:00:22,629 --> 00:00:26,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手一定会流泪的 为我而流泪</font>

2
00:00:28,499 --> 00:00:32,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以我本想在那艘船上和你道别的 真是的…</font>

3
00:00:34,619 --> 00:00:37,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你也太喜欢我了吧</font>

4
00:00:41,729 --> 00:00:45,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这3年一直拉着你到处跑 真是对不起</font>

5
00:00:47,179 --> 00:00:51,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如果可以的话 我还想继续看你那一边说「不讲道理」</font>

6
00:00:51,239 --> 00:00:53,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一边唉声叹气的侧脸</font>

7
00:00:55,759 --> 00:00:59,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你的笑脸 我永远不会看腻</font>

8
00:01:02,029 --> 00:01:04,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真是…不想死啊</font>

9
00:01:12,069 --> 00:01:12,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是</font>

10
00:01:14,479 --> 00:01:16,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那时候我答应过你</font>

11
00:01:17,469 --> 00:01:21,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不管你因为你的体质 被牵扯到多大的案子和麻烦之中</font>

12
00:01:22,179 --> 00:01:23,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我都会保护你</font>

13
00:01:25,199 --> 00:01:30,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以你就像现在这样 安心地睡吧</font>

14
00:01:34,439 --> 00:01:39,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然你下次醒来的时候 已经看不到我了</font>

15
00:01:40,899 --> 00:01:41,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没事的</font>

16
00:01:42,849 --> 00:01:47,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">她一定会代替我帮助你 而且…</font>

17
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:52,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也会代替我紧紧拥抱你</font>

18
00:01:55,109 --> 00:01:57,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">结果还是没来得及送给她</font>

19
00:02:03,009 --> 00:02:04,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还要先想个名字</font>

20
00:02:07,199 --> 00:02:13,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">封印了赫尔的意识 让这个肉体脱胎换骨的新名字…</font>

21
00:02:17,729 --> 00:02:18,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 助手</font>

22
00:02:19,609 --> 00:02:20,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要记住哦</font>

23
00:02:21,859 --> 00:02:26,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将来 那个把你从沉睡中唤醒的人叫…</font>

24
00:02:30,619 --> 00:02:33,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(第12集 和你一起度过的那耀眼的三年)</font>

25
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:34,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">1年没看到你的脸了 感觉眼神变得有些凶了啊
(第12集 和你一起度过的那耀眼的三年)</font>

26
00:02:34,629 --> 00:02:39,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">1年没看到你的脸了 感觉眼神变得有些凶了啊</font>

27
00:02:41,659 --> 00:02:45,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而你是从外表到内在都换了个遍啊</font>

28
00:02:48,859 --> 00:02:52,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你还在「心」里吧</font>

29
00:02:53,269 --> 00:02:56,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我只是稍微借她的身体一用</font>

30
00:02:56,939 --> 00:02:59,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">可没想过要鸠占鹊巢</font>

31
00:03:06,279 --> 00:03:09,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过 能见你一面我就很高兴了 谢丝塔</font>

32
00:03:17,279 --> 00:03:22,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔 先别闲聊了 要先把那家伙解决掉</font>

33
00:03:23,139 --> 00:03:26,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是啊 我就是为此而来的</font>

34
00:03:27,699 --> 00:03:28,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那么</font>

35
00:03:32,429 --> 00:03:35,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你来当我的助手吧</font>

36
00:03:38,019 --> 00:03:40,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好 乐意听命</font>

37
00:03:43,119 --> 00:03:44,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大侦探</font>

38
00:03:46,769 --> 00:03:47,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给</font>

39
00:03:49,829 --> 00:03:50,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">来了</font>

40
00:04:07,239 --> 00:04:09,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">咦 你要选那边啊？</font>

41
00:04:10,189 --> 00:04:12,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯？有什么问题吗</font>

42
00:04:13,239 --> 00:04:19,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这家伙已经没法攻击我了 由我负责正面比较好吧</font>

43
00:04:20,339 --> 00:04:21,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">都忘了</font>

44
00:04:22,539 --> 00:04:25,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没想到你这犯傻的毛病还没改</font>

45
00:04:36,129 --> 00:04:37,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说起来 一直都是这样啊</font>

46
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:40,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">放话说「今天要住进度假区酒店」</font>

47
00:04:40,959 --> 00:04:44,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">意气风发地冲进赌场 把身上的钱都押上去</font>

48
00:04:47,679 --> 00:04:51,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还不是因为你一直哭喊著「再也不想在野外上大号啦！」</font>

49
00:04:51,689 --> 00:04:53,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我才不得不想着发横财的吗！</font>

50
00:04:54,739 --> 00:04:56,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不许捏造记忆</font>

51
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:57,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如果是说我偶然遇到你在野外上…</font>

52
00:04:59,069 --> 00:05:05,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在户外给土地施肥 伤害到了你的自尊 我倒是可以道歉</font>

53
00:05:05,229 --> 00:05:08,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还在战斗呢！不要想起一些多余的事！</font>

54
00:05:15,139 --> 00:05:19,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且你不也有在我面前露出过难为情的样子吗！</font>

55
00:05:20,109 --> 00:05:21,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说什么呢？</font>

56
00:05:24,489 --> 00:05:28,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就是当初我们一起躺在床上…</font>

57
00:05:28,559 --> 00:05:31,139
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">啊 风好大听不清</font>

58
00:05:31,139 --> 00:05:33,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那就不要把枪指着我啊！</font>

59
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:42,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你忘了还在战斗？别让我想起多余的事</font>

60
00:05:42,779 --> 00:05:45,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是我该说的啊</font>

61
00:05:46,189 --> 00:05:47,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不讲道理</font>

62
00:05:58,869 --> 00:05:59,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那么</font>

63
00:06:00,939 --> 00:06:03,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">结果到底怎么样了？</font>

64
00:06:03,729 --> 00:06:04,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">什么怎么样？</font>

65
00:06:05,159 --> 00:06:06,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以 那个…</font>

66
00:06:06,709 --> 00:06:09,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一起睡在床上之后 我们…</font>

67
00:06:11,149 --> 00:06:11,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好上了？</font>

68
00:06:12,999 --> 00:06:16,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不是不愿想起多余的事吗</font>

69
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:21,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 其实我就是因为在意这个才停留于人世不去的</font>

70
00:06:22,269 --> 00:06:24,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你把重逢时的感动还给我</font>

71
00:06:26,199 --> 00:06:29,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那么 你到底是回来干什么的？</font>

72
00:06:51,879 --> 00:06:53,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">糟糕了</font>

73
00:07:15,359 --> 00:07:17,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">希望我来救你</font>

74
00:07:19,859 --> 00:07:23,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实是她这么求我的</font>

75
00:07:24,989 --> 00:07:26,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">夏凪求你？</font>

76
00:07:28,159 --> 00:07:32,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对 其实我本来都想把所有事都交给她了</font>

77
00:07:33,539 --> 00:07:37,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过这是最后一次 下不为例了</font>

78
00:07:40,459 --> 00:07:42,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 我知道</font>

79
00:07:45,239 --> 00:07:45,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手</font>

80
00:08:00,349 --> 00:08:01,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">身体在天空中飞舞</font>

81
00:08:03,269 --> 00:08:06,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那时候 谢丝塔也是这么救我的</font>

82
00:08:12,709 --> 00:08:15,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 不只是那个时候</font>

83
00:08:16,769 --> 00:08:21,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不管在何时 何地 我都被你…</font>

84
00:08:25,069 --> 00:08:29,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">看来我还是喜欢被你拉着到处跑啊</font>

85
00:08:32,089 --> 00:08:33,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么突然说这个 助手</font>

86
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不舍得我？</font>

87
00:08:39,389 --> 00:08:41,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我可没那么纠结于过去</font>

88
00:08:44,169 --> 00:08:44,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对不起</font>

89
00:08:46,749 --> 00:08:47,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">别道歉</font>

90
00:08:48,499 --> 00:08:50,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">先你而死 对不起</font>

91
00:08:51,389 --> 00:08:52,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">都说别道歉了</font>

92
00:08:57,719 --> 00:09:01,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实我当初没想过要和你一起旅行那么多年</font>

93
00:09:03,189 --> 00:09:05,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">结果一不留神就3年过去了</font>

94
00:09:07,739 --> 00:09:12,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我肯定是比我自己想的还要中意你吧</font>

95
00:09:13,819 --> 00:09:19,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">蠢货 我和你又不是情侣 连朋友都算不上</font>

96
00:09:20,239 --> 00:09:24,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只是侦探和助手…一对古怪的商业伙伴罢了</font>

97
00:09:24,819 --> 00:09:32,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我知道 你不觉得我有什么特别 我也不会对你另眼相看</font>

98
00:09:34,359 --> 00:09:34,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只是</font>

99
00:09:35,979 --> 00:09:39,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和你一起度过的那耀眼的三年</font>

100
00:09:40,589 --> 00:09:43,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是我最宝贵的回忆</font>

101
00:09:50,469 --> 00:09:52,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你是笨蛋吗</font>

102
00:09:56,329 --> 00:09:58,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对着一个死人倔强有什么用</font>

103
00:09:59,499 --> 00:10:02,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这1年里 辛苦你独自努力了</font>

104
00:10:21,539 --> 00:10:22,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说我不舍得？</font>

105
00:10:25,239 --> 00:10:31,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">抱歉 我身边可是有一堆吵闹的人 让我没空去想这事</font>

106
00:10:32,539 --> 00:10:34,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以我已经不孤独了</font>

107
00:10:35,819 --> 00:10:38,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗 要和她们好好相处哦</font>

108
00:10:41,439 --> 00:10:42,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 谢丝塔</font>

109
00:10:43,089 --> 00:10:43,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">什么？</font>

110
00:10:45,149 --> 00:10:50,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就是刚才说的 我们一起躺在床上之后的事</font>

111
00:10:51,659 --> 00:10:55,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">应该说很遗憾吧 什么都没发生哦</font>

112
00:10:56,719 --> 00:10:57,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗</font>

113
00:10:58,759 --> 00:11:00,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实我觉得</font>

114
00:11:02,469 --> 00:11:07,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如果是你的话 一次我还是能接受的</font>

115
00:11:09,649 --> 00:11:14,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这么重要的事情 下次要早点说啊</font>

116
00:11:34,249 --> 00:11:36,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你见到女士了？</font>

117
00:11:36,959 --> 00:11:41,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是啊 没她的话我们现在已经沉到海底了</font>

118
00:11:41,939 --> 00:11:46,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗 我们又被女士拯救了</font>

119
00:11:50,539 --> 00:11:51,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也许女士她…</font>

120
00:11:52,739 --> 00:11:57,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">早就知道自己会在那一天死去了</font>

121
00:11:57,689 --> 00:11:59,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 也许吧</font>

122
00:12:01,029 --> 00:12:04,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是 就算真的是这样 我也…</font>

123
00:12:04,989 --> 00:12:07,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">希望她能活下来</font>

124
00:12:12,619 --> 00:12:14,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">女士说了什么吗？</font>

125
00:12:15,449 --> 00:12:17,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要我和你们好好相处</font>

126
00:12:18,579 --> 00:12:19,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗</font>

127
00:12:21,249 --> 00:12:23,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">下次陪我去花店吧</font>

128
00:12:24,099 --> 00:12:24,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">花店？</font>

129
00:12:25,369 --> 00:12:28,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">告诉我哪些花适合用来给女士扫墓</font>

130
00:12:34,059 --> 00:12:36,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(日本 东京都 斋川唯)</font>

131
00:12:36,979 --> 00:12:37,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(男装店)</font>

132
00:12:37,799 --> 00:12:40,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真的就买这件吗？
(男装店)</font>

133
00:12:40,019 --> 00:12:40,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(男装店)</font>

134
00:12:40,719 --> 00:12:42,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 够了</font>

135
00:12:42,489 --> 00:12:44,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但这衣服很普通啊</font>

136
00:12:45,369 --> 00:12:50,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">君冢你从里到外都很普通 要是连衣服都普通</font>

137
00:12:50,799 --> 00:12:52,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就会和景色同化了啊</font>

138
00:12:52,949 --> 00:12:54,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么可能啊</font>

139
00:12:57,179 --> 00:12:58,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我看到了</font>

140
00:12:59,179 --> 00:13:01,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">看到了君冢成为龙套的未来</font>

141
00:13:01,819 --> 00:13:02,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂！</font>

142
00:13:04,619 --> 00:13:05,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真是的</font>

143
00:13:08,339 --> 00:13:14,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你一直用你的左眼看着我吧 多亏了你啊 斋川</font>

144
00:13:15,019 --> 00:13:16,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这不过是我该做的事而已</font>

145
00:13:17,209 --> 00:13:20,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为我是助手的助手啊</font>

146
00:13:25,039 --> 00:13:27,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">话说 你出现在这里真的没问题吗？</font>

147
00:13:28,149 --> 00:13:31,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不是说有一个用来感谢你的派对？</font>

148
00:13:32,469 --> 00:13:36,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 其实我已经跟他们说不要那么麻烦了</font>

149
00:13:36,939 --> 00:13:42,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">毕竟你可是他们的救命恩人 多亏了你 才能平安返航</font>

150
00:13:45,509 --> 00:13:48,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">啊 糟糕 到彩排时间了</font>

151
00:13:49,409 --> 00:13:50,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">彩排？</font>

152
00:13:51,089 --> 00:13:53,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">派对上有我的演唱会</font>

153
00:13:54,309 --> 00:13:55,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我希望在发生了那样的事件之后</font>

154
00:13:56,009 --> 00:13:59,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大家能多一些快乐的回忆</font>

155
00:14:00,579 --> 00:14:06,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且 软弱的人更容易被笑容和音乐感染</font>

156
00:14:06,749 --> 00:14:09,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是一个让我的信徒…</font>

157
00:14:09,819 --> 00:14:11,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不对 是粉丝增加的好机会！</font>

158
00:14:12,639 --> 00:14:14,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">斋川…</font>

159
00:14:14,009 --> 00:14:18,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好 世界最可爱偶像斋川唯大显身手的时候到了！</font>

160
00:14:26,729 --> 00:14:27,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">风靡小姐</font>

161
00:14:32,579 --> 00:14:33,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么说</font>

162
00:14:35,829 --> 00:14:38,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那件事我还没告诉夏凪呢</font>

163
00:14:40,129 --> 00:14:40,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗</font>

